{"tid":727554,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"不必再罵我　賤朗瞬間擁有 若是痛恨我　未珍惜過　我會自言自語中　說我沒錯","createTime":"2018-07-03T06:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T05:26:37.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"41d471edbaba78d32cc4474300432aef61158f24","tid":727554,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:08:39.000Z","msg":"誰終於得美斯也好　誰終歸巴塞更不需仰慕<br />\n若太在意這名詞　躲於歧途　未免失色得太早<br />\n<br />\n誰衝不開妳的領土　願妳亦讓我傾訴<br />\n渡過落泊的沿途不需酬勞　就盼今生今世終會能遇到<br />\n<br />\n尚未淌淚隨便即管　嘲笑我　亦未甘願隨著漆黑中熔化<br />\n<br />\n不須停留　不必再罵朗倔強濫用自由<br />\n若賤格但無內疚　是朗為信念　賤朗最新的藉口<br />\n不需回頭　不必再罵我　賤朗瞬間擁有<br />\n若是痛恨我　未珍惜過　我會自言自語中　說我沒錯"},{"pid":"f39008e890dccd491deb2a2a42ef0314f340d6d5","tid":727554,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"若是痛恨朗　未飛機過　賤朗自言自語中　說沒射錯"},{"pid":"97058fc59c48e68fab60ad9cc1efc10e9ae975d9","tid":727554,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:31:50.000Z","msg":"咩歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62332f680a1486e96962aaad1e9f222a86c2d916","tid":727554,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97058fc59c48e68fab60ad9cc1efc10e9ae975d9","tid":727554,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:31:50.000Z","msg":"咩歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:39:58.000Z","msg":"末賤種的呼聲"},{"pid":"406b44f2a13bb35f0f4d67b3e9d22751f4e6799f","tid":727554,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702f855fa414008d7ad50a322c1533c6798449b6","tid":727554,"uid":58022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"富士山下？"}]}